title: Second Date Update: Weak in the Knees
itunes:title: Second Date Update: Weak in the Knees
description: The guy on the phone today got "the invite" into his date's house as their night came to an end...But 20 minutes later...He was driving himself home and NOTHING romantic had happened... Now he wants our help finding out what ruined it in that short amount of time!
